---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Instrumetriq"
  description="Privacy Policy for Instrumetriq"
>
  <article>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 16, 2025</p>
    
    <section>
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        This privacy policy describes how Instrumetriq handles information in relation to our
        website and dataset.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
      <p>
        Our website does not collect personal information from visitors. We may use standard
        web analytics to understand site usage patterns.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>3. Dataset Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        The sentiment dataset is collected from publicly available social media data. All data
        is anonymized and de-identified to protect user privacy. Personal identifiable information
        is removed during the collection process.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        If we use third-party services (such as hosting or analytics), those services may have
        their own privacy policies that govern their use of information.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>5. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through the information
        provided on our Contact page.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  article {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .last-updated {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
</style>
